    • importMeshDataAdjacencyMatrix

      public void importMeshDataAdjacencyMatrix​(java.io.File obj, java.io.File txt) throws java.io.IOException
      From an .obj and .txt file exported from MorphoGraphX, store each vertex and face into respective ArrayLists. Marginally faster, but tends to not be worth it as datasets large enough for the speedup to be appreciable may be too large to store the adjacency matrix in memory.
      Parameters:
      obj - obj file path
      txt - txt file path
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - Throws IOException

    • generateSurfacesAdjacencyMatrix

      public void generateSurfacesAdjacencyMatrix​(int size)
      Generates a list of discrete connected surfaces. Marginally faster, but tends to not be worth it as datasets large enough for the speedup to be appreciable may be too large to store the adjacency matrix in memory.
      Parameters:
      size - vertex threshold value below which a surface will not be added to the list

    • determineInteriorPoints

      public void determineInteriorPoints()
      Generates a 3D integer array of interior points by counting the number of intersections a line cast from each point in the sample space in the Z-direction has with the faces of the surfaces. An odd number of intersection means a point is in the interior of a surface. Even means exterior.
